<article id="post-1554" class="post-1554 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-cli category-getopt category-perl tag-perl tag-cli tag-getopt">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Getopt modules 15:&nbsp;MooX::Options</h1>

		<div class="entry-meta">
			Posted on <a href="https://perlancar.wordpress.com/2016/12/15/getopt-modules-15-mooxoptions/" title="12:00 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2016-12-15T00:00:00+00:00" pubdate>15 December 2016</time></a><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://perlancar.wordpress.com/author/perlancar/" title="View all posts by perlancar" rel="author">perlancar</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><B>About this mini-article series.</B> Each day for 24 days, I will be reviewing a module that parses command-line options (such module is usually under the <TT>Getopt::*</TT> namespace). <A HREF="https://perlancar.wordpress.com/2016/12/01/getopt-modules-01-getoptlong/">First article is here</A>. <A HREF="https://perlancar.wordpress.com/2016/12/14/getopt-modules-14-moosexgetopt/">Previous article</A>. </p>
<p><A HREF="https://metacpan.org/pod/MooX::Options">MooX::Options</A> (written by <A HREF="https://metacpan.org/author/celogeek">celogeek</A> in 2011 and still being actively maintained) is roughly equivalent to <A HREF="https://metacpan.org/pod/MooseX::Getopt">MooseX::Getopt</A> (or more correctly to <A HREF="https://metacpan.org/pod/MooseX::Getopt::Strict">MooseX::Getopt::Strict</A>). </p>
<p>Here are the users of the module on CPAN (34, not as many as MooseX::Getopt at 94, but MooseX::Getopt has a 4 year lead): </p>
<p><PRE CLASS="fixed_width_section">% lcpan rdeps MooX::Options<br />
+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-+<br />
| phase   | rel      | dist                                | author    | dist_version | req_version |<br />
+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;+&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-+<br />
| runtime | requires | Acme-CatFS                          | PACMAN    | 0.002        | 0           |<br />
| runtime | requires | App-Antigen                         | TBSLIVER  | 0.001        | 0           |<br />
